# MF-4: Root Cause Analysis
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: Recurring issues and defects

## CATEGORY CONTEXT
- Root Cause Analysis: Process to identify underlying causes of recurring issues.

ENFORCE: Recurring issues must have a documented root cause and action plan before the fix is accepted.
PROHIBIT: Repeated patching of symptoms without investigation.
ON VIOLATION: Escalate unresolved recurring issues to engineering leadership.
